Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mesto Meadrich lost his Crest\Nand his territories, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And to whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A wandering Lord by the name of Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he's making it known that he's joining\Nthe Alliance rather than the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just when we're on the brink of war,\Na Crest and territoy come falling into our laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No time to lose, we move to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no objections...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're talking about\Na cross-border invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lords of Clovis will be sure\Nto give you an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once I seize that Crest and land,\Nit won't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can take one wandering Lord in my sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me that\Nall this territory is mine now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The three villages in this territory\Nhave recognized you as their Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They welcome you, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they were being taxed too heavily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to collect taxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not how it works.\NYou'll need funds to run your territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was a court rank\Nhigh enough to govern my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of court rank,\Nyou've likely met that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I have no idea how big your village is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small, impoverished town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We struggle just to survive there.\NAnd still, too many end up dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take it anymore, so I left the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you see that as having fled\Nyour hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you suspect that becoming stronger\Nto save your village is just an excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that sets my mind at ease a little.\NI'll stoop to any means to achieve my goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you were the overly scrupulous type,\NLord Theo, that might not sit well with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are the neighboring Lords up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, they're all vying\Nto be the first to seize this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd be worried otherwise. We wouldn't\Nstand a chance if they joined forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think will make the first move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord whose territory lies to the east.\NThe ruler of Savis, Lassic David, I would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's of modest means,\Nhe's extremely ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's already bolstered his troops for battle,\Nand even hired some mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should we bring in\Nsome mercenaries of our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under these circumstances,\NI doubt anyone decent would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crazy about the idea,\Nbut I'm considering calling a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca, you have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!\NDon't look so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to continue monitoring our territory\Nand what's brewing nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may not have time to rest,\Nbut I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted that the moment\NI decided to serve you, Lady Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I knew you'd run me into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our worlds exist infinitely,\Nand shall never intersect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, dimensions will distort,\Ncasting a shadow onto a parallel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Converge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cait Sith of Tír Na nÓg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Sir Balgary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I grant you permission to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And to rub me behind my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you summon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to deliver a message\Nto Aishela for her to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That woman makes me uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I will thank you with\Nall your favorite foods on your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I shall carry out your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see things look pretty hectic here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since there's no telling when\Na neighboring Lord will attack us, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your intention in all this, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of get that you didn't want\Nto enter a contract with the Lord of Artuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, I didn't want\Na contract with anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:07:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those Lords always lust for Crests and power,\Nso it's a vicious cycle of conspiracy and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that whoever completes\Nthe Emperor's Holy Seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and restores order to this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...must be someone like the First Lord Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the legendary hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A Lord like Leon,\Nwho will never lose sight of his ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's who I wish to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but my ideals are pretty trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trivial?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to bring bliss to an entire village\Nis not trivial at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And my goal is to make sure that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what's in it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to revel in my own talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I've gained power, and I never\Nforget my ideals, you'll be fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I'll leave everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the first step toward my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy seized Meadrich's castle\Nwith scant numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they've got some\Nskilled ones on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we're talking sword skills,\NI'm no slouch either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Behold the might of\Nthese fifty expert troops I've trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus five mercenaries in the fold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These forces are more than you can afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, you did give up most of\Nthe fortune your predecessor built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to take Meadrich's land\Nto make the money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going all-in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you lose, it all goes down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to win. Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The issue is our opponents also have a mage.\NSo you're gonna have to pitch in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca Meletes, right?\NI happen to know that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, sure, she's gifted,\Nbut nowhere near my level!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I saw something special\Nin a mage like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreno, I'm asking you\Nto lend me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mobilize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here they come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I don't have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Now I know the battle's a surefire win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you actually have a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was my senior\Nwhen we were apprentices.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though, in the end,\Nshe never did become a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Balgary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Theo, this is Aishela, an Artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who are you? What are you to Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the unfortunate Lord\Nshe's under contract to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You signed on with a loser like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo happens to have\Nmagnificent ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Such magnificent ideals, and uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh! My poor Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm won't ask why Siluca\Nwould serve someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you do anything unsavory to her\Njust because you're her master,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live. I saw stars for\Na moment, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sir Balgary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll become king of the Cait Siths one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See to it that you make no blunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucerne Hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're my choice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with the outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything else\Nthat's easy to move in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're adorable no matter what you wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not see the enemy mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's using an Invisibility Spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's planning to swoop in\Nand attack after evaluating the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aishela, to the right. Irvin, take center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll thwart them from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The earth is unmoving.\NYet is not invariably so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sea becomes land,\Nthe land becomes mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surge forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You evaded that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to go a bit deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be doing well, little Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was he targeting me from the start?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While you dawdle here,\Nyour Lord could get himself defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware of the situation.\NYou've got some formidable allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I take you hostage,\Nvictory will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm hard to beat\Nin situations like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well surrender, little Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really think I'd surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abjuration Magic, huh?\NBut how long you can keep it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're already spent after just this,\Nit proves you have no talent as a mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to guide you to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke her without thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is to make short work of them\Nso I can go to Siluca's aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your doing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You put up a good fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pierce her by going through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond annoying...\NBut I think I like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When this battle's over, let's be friends, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Are you a Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a footman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the toughest one to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Gluck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hoo-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought,\Nit didn't work on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem pretty winded, little Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you.\NYour strikes are becoming more labored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, then I'll end this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This may be my first battlefield,\Nbut even I can tell which side is losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should've made my move sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, as your Lord, this is my battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess you have\Nno intention of surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think you can beat me\Nwith these skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you're beginning to stumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not now... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...allow myself to lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you attack, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I haven't found any openings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, allow me to–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of the neighboring nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have captured your mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moreno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:19:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Lassic wouldn't even flinch\Nover having his mage caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to become your subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subordinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can go ahead and accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you throwing away your ambition?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we serve this Lord, we'll never\Nbe defeated at the hands our neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we play our cards right, Savis, Clovis,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as well as Forvis to the south,\Ncould all be conquered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My ambition is not to become emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm serving another,\Nbeing able to reign over one nation is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your ambition is so paltry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I'm capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's something I can't do alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I brought you onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Lassic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're under contract\Nto a fine Lord yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That robe certainly becomes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Lassic, I accept your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Lassic David, offer my Crest\Nto you as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Theo, accept they Crest\Nand receive it as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Theo has reached\Nthe court rank of Baron,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and a subordinate Crest\Nhas been granted to Sir Lassic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AMBITION
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is prone to audacious action.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How would you have me deal with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think an ignorant girl\Nwould dare insult you, Lord Villar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you start by investigating\Nwhat her motivations could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if necessary, proceed to punish her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:22:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you have a drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I truly appreciate the offer, my Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this issue with the Meletes girl\Nis of utmost urgency.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No other man worships women as much as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why can't anyone live up\Nto my expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting a woman like my mother\Nis no small feat, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 3:\NBATTLE FLAG
